  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BEFORE YOU BUY! [ A Short Game! ]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Before They Wake</strong> is a gripping third-person horror experience set in the 1980s. Step into the shoes of Alfred Baptiste as he embarks on a desperate quest for solace and a cure for a mutating virus. This virus has caused him temporary paraplegia, gradually impairing his mobility and strength. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126110/extras/85ca86bcf2ccb563f5b1937f0b537efe.poster.avif?t=1730883019\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126110/extras/85ca86bcf2ccb563f5b1937f0b537efe.webm?t=1730883019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126110/extras/85ca86bcf2ccb563f5b1937f0b537efe.mp4?t=1730883019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you’ll explore a series of tapes documenting Alfred's journey from the onset of his paralysis to his relentless fight for survival and a cure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126110/extras/b9f1e76f0b59ef88be6a5e7832e7ee3d.poster.avif?t=1730883019\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126110/extras/b9f1e76f0b59ef88be6a5e7832e7ee3d.webm?t=1730883019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126110/extras/b9f1e76f0b59ef88be6a5e7832e7ee3d.mp4?t=1730883019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a journey into a mysterious realm where beauty and horror intertwine. Drive your truck through breathtaking yet unsettling landscapes, where every corner hides a new secret and the line between wonder and dread is dangerously thin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126110/extras/8cfd8927562257bfa48c98310ef70b8f.poster.avif?t=1730883019\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126110/extras/8cfd8927562257bfa48c98310ef70b8f.webm?t=1730883019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126110/extras/8cfd8927562257bfa48c98310ef70b8f.mp4?t=1730883019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover a world where beauty and horror intertwine. Every stunning scene hides a hint of fear, making every moment a puzzle of wonder and dread. Unravel the mysteries as you navigate this captivating and chilling landscape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WATCH HIS TAPES AND SAVE ALFRED!</strong></p>",
